1 (f) This section does not apply to a moratorium related to a watershed
2 or other body of water instituted by rule before the effective date of this
3 section.
4
5 SECTION 3. DO NOT CODIFY. Existing rule.
6 The Department of Agriculture shall utilize the current Arkansas
7 Pollution Control and Ecology Commission's rules on Liquid Animal Waste
8 Management Systems, 8 CAR pt. 24, formerly known as Regulation No. 5, to
9 administer the department's authority over liquid animal waste management
10 systems under § 15-20-102 until the department adopts final rules regarding
11 liquid animal waste management systems.
12
13 SECTION 4. DO NOT CODIFY. Effective date.
14 This act shall be effective on and after February 1, 2026.
